    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1060698/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">安然</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-12-06"
      class="main-meta">2007-12-06 21:11:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1254150_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在飞机上一往一返中,读了二本关于各人喜好或言收藏的书:王世襄的《自珍集》和黎坚惠的《时装时刻》。  王世襄的家世渊源,生活年代让他的收藏品即杂面广又显学识博古。曾看过文章说王世襄精通的东西远不止于《自珍集》所例。但是《自珍集》中大半东西已是我闻所未闻抑或意料不到...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1254150/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1254150_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1254150_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评10篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
